OL,3,CMan, 20, jailed for causing the death
OL,4,Cof his girlfriend in car crash
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for driving
OL,7,F"dangerously fast" and bringing
OL,8,F"carnage" to a family after causing
OL,9,Fthe death of his girlfriend in a car
OL,10,Fcrash in Shropshire.
OL,12,FLogan Addison, from Market Drayton,
OL,13,Fwas found guilty of causing death by
OL,14,Fdangerous driving at Shrewsbury Crown
OL,15,FCourt.
OL,17,FLily-May Vaughan, who was 17, was a
OL,18,Fpassenger in the vehicle being driven
OL,19,Fby Logan Addison, who is now 20, when
OL,20,Fit came off the road near Shawbury
OL,21,FHeath on February 4th, 2023.
