OL,3,CMan, 20, jailed for causing the death
OL,4,Cof his girlfriend in car crash
OL,6,FAddison was jailed for five-and-a-half
OL,7,Fyears and was also banned from driving
OL,8,Ffor eight years, commencing on his
OL,9,Frelease from prison.
OL,11,FThe 20-year-old had been driving 'at
OL,12,Fspeed' when he lost control and hit an
OL,13,Felectricity pole. Lily-May died at the
OL,14,Fscene.
OL,16,FWhat was said at the trial?
