OL,3,CMan, 20, jailed for causing the death
OL,4,Cof his girlfriend in car crash
OL,6,FDuring the week-long trial, which was
OL,7,Fheld in April, Addison maintained a
OL,8,Fstory that he lost control of his
OL,9,Fvehicle when he swerved to avoid
OL,10,Fanother car.
OL,12,FHowever, witnesses said they saw
OL,13,FAddison, who was 17 at the time of the
OL,14,Fincident, driving at speed and
OL,15,Fdangerously before the collision
OL,16,Fhappened.
OL,18,FHe was found guilty, and the judge
OL,19,Findicated he would get a significant
OL,20,Fcustodial sentence.
