OL,3,CMan, 20, jailed for causing the death
OL,4,Cof his girlfriend in car crash
OL,6,FThe court heard how seven weeks after
OL,7,Fcommitting the offence in March 2023,
OL,8,FAddison was charged with driving
OL,9,Fwithout insurance and driving without
OL,10,Fdue care and attention.
OL,12,FThis was after he filmed himself
OL,13,Fwheelspinning his car and driving
OL,14,Faround a Tesco's car park in
OL,15,FShrewsbury, saying "guess who's back
OL,16,Fon the road?"
OL,18,FLeanne Vaughan, Lily May's mum told
OL,19,FITV News Central 'she never thought
OL,20,Fthis would happen to her'
