OL,3,CMan, 20, jailed for causing the death
OL,4,Cof his girlfriend in car crash
OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement, her mum
OL,7,Fsaid: "Lily-May was quite simply a
OL,8,Fremarkable young lady- full of life,
OL,9,Fpositive."
OL,11,FShe added: "It's a real loss to the
OL,12,Fworld that Lily-May has passed.
OL,14,F"It is against the natural order of
OL,15,Fthings for a mother to lose a child at
OL,16,Fthe age of 17."
OL,18,F'The loss of Lily will always be a
OL,19,Flife sentence for me'
