OL,3,CMan, 20, jailed for causing the death
OL,4,Cof his girlfriend in car crash
OL,6,FHer mum said: "When you look at the
OL,7,Fresearch and the science, it proves
OL,8,Fthat 17-year-olds' brains aren't fully
OL,9,Fdeveloped, so they will take risks
OL,10,Fwith passengers. I firmly believe that
OL,11,Fif the law had said that drivers
OL,12,Fcouldn't carry passengers, then Lily-
OL,13,FMay might still be here today."
OL,15,FIn his sentencing remarks, Judge Deni
OL,16,FMatthews said to Logan Addison: "You
OL,17,Fwere driving ridiculously fast,
OL,18,Fdangerously fast in what is in effect
OL,19,Fa country lane.
