OL,3,CMan, 20, jailed for causing the death
OL,4,Cof his girlfriend in car crash
OL,6,F"Your driving brought disruption,
OL,7,Fdestruction, and carnage to the family
OL,8,Fof a beautiful young woman."
OL,10,FWest Mercia Police Chief Inspector
OL,11,FJulian Smith spoke to ITV News Central
OL,12,Fabout the investigation.
OL,14,FWest Mercia Police, Chief Inspector
OL,15,FJulian Smith said: "We are pleased
OL,16,Fwith the sentence handed to Addison
OL,17,Ftoday, and hope it sends a strong
OL,18,Fmessage to anyone who thinks driving
OL,19,Fdangerously is acceptable.
