OL,6,F"Unfortunately Lily-May was waved off
OL,7,Fone day and taken from her family with
OL,8,Fno notice, it's far too common on the
OL,9,Froads, driving is a privilege and not
OL,10,Fa right and when we drive cars we need
OL,11,Fto drive them with due care and
OL,12,Fattention and it's always an absolute
OL,13,Ftragedy when someone dies on the
OL,14,Froads."
